OL,3,CTeacher facing life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurder and sex abuse of adopted baby
OL,6,FA high school teacher is facing a
OL,7,Fmandatory life sentence for the murder
OL,8,Fof an adopted 13-month-old baby he
OL,9,Fsexually abused and treated as his
OL,10,F"plaything".
OL,12,FJamie Varley, 37, adopted Preston
OL,13,FDavey at nine months old with his
OL,14,Fpartner, ex-public schoolboy and
OL,15,Ffinancial sales manager John McGowan-
OL,16,FFazakerley, 32.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@KO]
