OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781842676
OL,3,CTeacher facing life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurder and sex abuse of adopted baby
OL,6,FIn the four months he was in their
OL,7,Fcare, Preston was routinely ill-
OL,8,Ftreated, had indecent images and
OL,9,Fvideos taken of him, and was sexually
OL,10,Fabused and physically assaulted,
OL,11,Fsuffering 40 traumatic injuries.
OL,13,FPreston had been taken from his
OL,14,Fmother, Sarah Davey, now 42, by an
OL,15,Femergency care order by Oldham Council.
OL,17,FMs Davey, when she was 14, had been
OL,18,Fjailed for the "unspeakably wicked"
OL,19,Fmurder of a frail pensioner in 1998
OL,20,Fand had been in and out of prison
OL,21,Fsince then.
OL,26,@zD@POUzD@cO]
