PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781842676
OL,3,CTeacher facing life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurder and sex abuse of adopted baby
OL,6,FVarley and McGowan-Fazakerley were
OL,7,Fapproved for adoption in January 2023
OL,8,Fand Preston began living at their home
OL,9,Fin Blackpool, Lancashire, in April
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FFollowing an eight-week trial both men
OL,13,Fwere convicted by a jury at Preston
OL,14,FCrown Court on Monday, 15 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
