FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781842676
OL,3,CTeacher facing life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurder and sex abuse of adopted baby
OL,6,FVarley was found guilty of murder, two
OL,7,Fcounts of assault by penetration, five
OL,8,Fcounts of cruelty to a child, grievous
OL,9,Fbodily harm, sexual assault of a
OL,10,Fchild, 13 counts of taking indecent
OL,11,Fphotos or videos of a child, one of
OL,12,Fdistributing an indecent photo of a
OL,13,Fchild, to his co-accused, and one of
OL,14,Fmaking an indecent photo.
OL,16,FMcGowan-Fazakerley was found guilty of
OL,17,Fallowing the death of a child, two
OL,18,Fcounts of child cruelty and one count
OL,19,Fof the sexual assault of a child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
