PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781842676
OL,3,CTeacher facing life sentence for
OL,4,Cmurder and sex abuse of adopted baby
OL,6,FThe trial heard Preston had been taken
OL,7,Fto Blackpool Victoria Hospital three
OL,8,Ftimes in the months before his death,
OL,9,Fon April 27 2023, and was seen by a
OL,10,F"battery of professionals" during his
OL,11,Flife, including multiple social
OL,12,Fworkers, health visitors and medics.
OL,14,FA social services investigation is
OL,15,Funder way. Mr Justice Turner will pass
OL,16,Fsentence on Thursday, 18 June.
OL,18,FWant more on the issues effecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
